                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Du souvenir et du remord,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! si l'Étoile de la Mort,\nA ses propres feux consumée,\nN'est plus l'hôtesse accoutumée\nDu souvenir et du remord,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Où fuirai-je, si l'étendue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "S'ouvre à mon vol sans le fermer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "S'il me faut à jamais t'aimer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Toi qui m'es à jamais perdue ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Où fuirai-je, si l'étendue\nS'ouvre à mon vol sans le fermer,\nS'il me faut à jamais t'aimer,\nToi qui m'es à jamais perdue ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Toi qui passes, rayonnes, luis",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Et fais vivant ce que tu touches,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Lumière de mes yeux farouches,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Où fuirai-je, si tu me fuis ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Toi qui passes, rayonnes, luis\nEt fais vivant ce que tu touches,\nLumière de mes yeux farouches,\nOù fuirai-je, si tu me fuis ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Où s'en va le vent qui m'emporte",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Où gît le repos de mon cœur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Puisque, sur ton chemin vainqueur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "L'Étoile de la Mort est morte !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Où s'en va le vent qui m'emporte\nOù gît le repos de mon cœur,\nPuisque, sur ton chemin vainqueur,\nL'Étoile de la Mort est morte !"
        }
    ],
